task.summary:
Change TwoLevelTreeTour::parents' type to std::list
None of the functions in TwoLevelTreeTour was tested!

Fixed a bug in TsplibProblem::trueDistance
and optimized the Lin-Kernighan-Algorithm to not always recalculate the current gain.
Fixed bug with the implicit copy-constructor of TwoLevelTreeTour

Fixed bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::isBetween
The case analysis was not complete. Also added groupSize = 30 for testing purposes (for n <= 1000) and an error if flip is called with illegal arguments.

Fixed a bug in TwoLevelTreeTour::flip
The comparison of sequence numbers needs to respect the reversal bit.

Refactored TwoLevelTreeTour::reverse
TwoLevelTreeTour::reverse has become TwoLevelTreeTour::SegmentParent:: reverseVertices and TwoLevelTreeTour::reverseParents. Also reordered some of the functions of TwoLevelTreeTour and added comments.
Fixed a bug in reverseVertices / reverseParents
Fixed a bug in flip, mergeHalfSegment and isBetween
Fixed a bug in TwoLevelTreeTour for small instances (<= 1000)

Added comments for TwoLevelTreeTour
Also added TODOs and improved visualize.py

Improved LinKernighanHeuristic
Eliminated repeated calls to predecessor(xi) and successor(xi)
Fixed a bug in flip caused by reverseParents
Improved Prim's algorithm and added comments
Added the LinKernighanHeuristic class to implement multiple trials

Added CandidateEdges::optimizedAlphaNearestNeighbors
Added CandidateEdges::rawNearestNeighbors Fixed bug in optimizedAlphaDistances (line 180/183) Fixed bug in OneTree::degrees (line 36) Refactored allVertices from std::vector to std::unordered_set
There is still a bug in optimizedAlphaDistances because the objective function should never exceed the length of the optimum tour
Fixed bug with unsigned types in AlphaDistances
Refactored CandidateEdges to not inherit from std::vector

Added command line options
The command line options are untested and --output-to-file and --verbose are not yet implemented

Implemented the command line options --output-to-file and --verbose
and also updated README

Added command line option --dont-store-distances
Fixed bug with --candidate-edges Updated README

Moved AlternatingWalk to Tour.h
AlternatingWalk does not inherit from std::vector anymore
Updated comments and variable names in Tour.h
